<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Our Service is not intended for children under 13 years of age (or 16 in some jurisdictions). We do not knowingly collect Personal Information from children. If we become aware of such collection, we will delete it promptly. If you believe we have collected data from a child, contact us immediately.</p>
